00:41:13,253 --> 00:41:16,589
Maaf. Aku takkan pulang larut malam lagi.

463
00:41:19,092 --> 00:41:20,385
Kamar 207.

464
00:41:21,719 --> 00:41:23,805
Ucapkan peraturan asrama.

465
00:41:24,430 --> 00:41:27,892
Patuhi jam malam, jangan memprotes,
jangan menginap di luar.

